```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant A as Agent
    participant L as LLM (pi-ai)
    participant T as Tool

    U->>A: prompt(message)
    A->>A: _runLoop(messages)
    A->>A: agent_start
    A->>A: turn_start
    A->>A: message_start (user)
    A->>A: message_end (user)
    
    A->>L: streamAssistantResponse()
    L-->>A: message_start (assistant partial)
    loop streaming
        L-->>A: text_delta / thinking_delta / toolcall_delta
        A-->>U: message_update (render)
    end
    L-->>A: done
    A->>A: final = response.result()
    A->>A: Append final assistant message
    A-->>U: message_end (assistant)

    alt assistant có tool calls
        A->>T: executeToolCalls()
        loop từng tool call
            A->>T: tool_execution_start
            T->>T: tool.execute()
            T-->>A: tool_execution_end (result)
            A->>A: Tạo ToolResultMessage
            A-->>U: message_start (toolResult)
            A-->>U: message_end (toolResult)
            Note over A,T: Sau mỗi tool, check steering
            alt steering có
                A->>A: pendingMessages = steering
                A->>T: skip còn lại (skipToolCall)
                break
            end
        end
        A-->>U: turn_end
    else không có tool calls
        A-->>U: turn_end
    end

    alt follow-up có (ngoài outer loop)
        A->>A: pendingMessages = follow-up
        A->>A: Outer loop tiếp tục (inner loop mới)
    elsekhông có
        A->>A: agent_end
        A-->>U: (Promise resolves)
    end
```

---

**Giải thích**:
- Sequence bắt đầu từ `agent.prompt(message)`.
- Inner loop: stream assistant, nếu có tools → execute tuần tự, sau mỗi tool check steering.
- Steering: interrupts, skip remaining tools, set pendingMessages để next turn ngay.
- Sau inner loop, outer loop check follow-up. Nếu có, outer loop tiếp tục (inner loop mới với pending messages).
- Nếu không, `agent_end`.
